#v(10pt)
*Q: _How did you find all of the information you needed?_*\
*A:* Usually I find everything on the Internet, using Google maps for finding interesting places and restaurants, social networks to find travel suggestions and confirm some of my ideas, comparative services like Booking for find cheap accommodations and so on. Although I don't like travel agencies, as I mentioned before, I still like to look what they offer: if something inspires me, then i use it as a good starting point for my researches.
#v(10pt)
*Q: _Was searching information difficult?_*\
