#v(10pt)
*Q: _How did you organize the journey?_*\
*A:* Over the year I've developed a precise method to plan everything: firstly I understand what I have to search; food, transport, accommodation and activities, then I use online services to find hotels, cheap typical restaurants and possible places to visit. Lastly, I use social networks and similar to find real travel tips: this is particularly important since I love to visit places less "touristy".
#v(10pt)
*Q: _How much time did it take?_*\
